{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013U7mLcLPS1Z9PiRpDLVRmJ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-21\n     2→\n     3→### 0-1-sprint-state-live-updates — verify (2026-03-21T07:55Z)\n     4→\n     5→- **Bug found and fixed:** `parseRalphStatus()` in `migration.ts` was missing the new `currentStory`, `currentPhase`, `lastAction`, `acProgress` fields added by this story. Migration test was failing. Fixed by adding null defaults to the return object.\n     6→- **Observability gap:** VictoriaLogs returned zero log events for all `codeharness progress` CLI invocations. The progress command doesn't emit structured logs.\n     7→\n     8→### 0-2-ralph-progress-display — verify (2026-03-21T08:00Z)\n     9→\n    10→- **Proof format issue:** AC3 initially reused evidence from AC2 without its own `bash` code block, causing `codeharness verify` to report 3/4 ACs. Fixed by adding a distinct bash block.\n    11→- **No BATS tests in container:** `ralph/tests/` not included in npm package. Verification relied on direct function invocation with mock data.\n    12→- **VictoriaLogs query syntax:** `_stream_id:*` pattern invalid for VictoriaLogs. Used `*` wildcard instead.\n    13→\n    14→### 0-3-run-command-dashboard — verify (2026-03-21T08:04Z)\n    15→\n    16→- **Minor format deviations:** Story specified checkmark/cross prefixes but implementation uses `[OK]`/`[FAIL]` tags. Functionally equivalent, passed verification.\n    17→- **Architecture difference:** Story specified `DashboardFormatter` class but implementation uses Ink React components. Same functionality, different design.\n    18→\n    19→### 0-5-1-stream-json-claude-driver — verify (2026-03-21T08:09Z)\n    20→\n    21→- Clean verification — all 4 ACs passed without issues.\n    22→\n    23→### 0-5-2-stream-event-parser — verify (2026-03-21T10:35Z)\n    24→\n    25→- **Infrastructure fix:** `parseStreamLine` was not exported from `src/index.ts`, making it inaccessible in the container's dist bundle. Added re-export to `src/index.ts` and rebuilt.\n    26→- **ESM import workaround:** Container requires `VITEST=1` env var to suppress CLI auto-parse on module import. Uses `node --input-type=module` for ESM.\n    27→- **[OBSERVABILITY GAP]** VictoriaLogs returned zero log events for all parser invocations — `parseStreamLine` is a pure function with no telemetry.\n    28→- **Non-standard status from previous session:** Sprint status had `verified` (not a valid status). Normalized to `verifying` before proceeding.\n    29→- All 6 ACs passed black-box verification after infrastructure fix.\n    30→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01WbghDLFsXiBxMyWVBJH7t1","session_id":"14bb9049-f41e-41a8-aff7-919131cd9a0b","uuid":"60f004f8-59cb-4803-8867-f7d2b42914fa","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:40:28.646Z"}
