{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AVJXjEUwnTYpVWoQFELJwF","type":"tool_result","content":"  1200→- **Session issues log is high-value:** Having every subagent write to `.session-issues.md` made this retrospective fast and accurate. Keep this pattern.\n  1201→\n  1202→---\n  1203→\n  1204→## 6. Action Items\n  1205→\n  1206→### Fix now\n  1207→- (none — all blocking issues were resolved during session)\n  1208→\n  1209→### Fix soon\n  1210→- Add `parseStreamLine` and `codeharness progress` to structured logging so VictoriaLogs verification is meaningful\n  1211→- Add an export verification step to the dev-story workflow — every new public function must appear in `src/index.ts`\n  1212→- Standardize sprint-status.yaml states: only allow `backlog`, `in-progress`, `verifying`, `done`, `blocked`, `flagged`\n  1213→- Include `ralph/tests/` in the npm package or provide an alternative path for BATS test verification in containers\n  1214→\n  1215→### Backlog\n  1216→- Decouple CLI auto-parse from ESM module loading so `VITEST=1` hack is not needed for container testing\n  1217→- Update story 0-3 spec to reflect Ink component architecture (retroactive doc fix)\n  1218→- Add structured telemetry to all pure utility functions (at minimum debug-level trace)\n  1219→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01WbghDLFsXiBxMyWVBJH7t1","session_id":"14bb9049-f41e-41a8-aff7-919131cd9a0b","uuid":"c8a18696-ebb8-40b8-b0a8-9e5868c96e77","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:40:49.629Z"}
